# RealChute's plugin assembly hard-depends on ClickThroughBlocker and ToolbarControl, so its
# part modules do not register unless both are installed alongside it; ClickThroughBlocker in
# turn references Harmony, whose absence otherwise crashes kRPC's assembly scanner at startup.
# All three are installed only as RealChute's dependencies, not requested on their own.
